Package: eidith
Title: Data access and analytical tools for the PREDICT EIDITH database
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Noam", "Ross", , "ross@ecohealthalliance.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Nistara", "Randhawa", , "nrandhawa@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Cale", "Basaraba", , "basaraba@ecohealthalliance.org", role = c("aut")),
    person("EcoHealth Alliance", role="cph"))
Description: This package provides a programmatic interface to the PREDICT
    EIDITH database from R, allowing download and query of sampling data.  Use
    of download functions requires an EIDITH account with appropriate permissions.
    EIDITH also generates standard reports and implements common analysis
    functions for PREDICT data.
